2.title: All Stars
2.plot: We've got the best-of-the-best from Season 1 and 2 of Laughs. Comedians including Ms. Pat, Steve Gillespie, Mia Jackson, K-von, Melissa Shoshahi, Brett Druck, Jarret Berenstein, Mike Paramore, Zoltan Kaszas, Delanie Fischer, Ryan Budds, Josh Adams and MORE!.

4.title: Laughs: Live from Pechanga!
